are 36, 77 and 67 degrees.</i>

11:28.354 --> 11:32.108
<i>Side A has a length of 12.8 cm.</i>

11:32.275 --> 11:36.279
<i>Side C has a length of 9.7 cm.</i>

11:36.529 --> 11:40.283
<i>Find the area of the triangle,
the length of side B...</i>

11:40.450 --> 11:41.951
<i>and the type of triangle.</i>

11:42.201 --> 11:43.536
<i>Good luck.</i>

11:44.913 --> 11:48.791
<i>The eyes of a fresh fish are not:</i>

11:49.209 --> 11:51.044
<i>A) Bleary,</i>

11:51.252 --> 11:52.879
<i>B) Big,</i>

11:53.087 --> 11:55.256
<i>C) Red.</i>

11:55.465 --> 11:56.966
<i>Good luck.</i>

11:58.927 --> 12:05.141
<i>If for any reason
we are still awake at 11:00 p.m.,</i>

12:05.391 --> 12:07.810
<i>what kind of procedure do we follow?</i>

12:09.479 --> 12:10.980
<i>Good luck.</i>

13:06.786 --> 13:08.955
- Are you ready?
- Yes.

13:09.330 --> 13:11.708
- Shall I wait for you?
- Yes.

13:18.298 --> 13:20.675
- How do I look?
- Just fine.

13:21.551 --> 13:22.552
Now?

13:24.053 --> 13:25.722
That's fine, too.

13:27.807 --> 13:31.060
I don't think the skirt goes 
with this shirt.

13:35.231 --> 13:37.817
- How many do you have?
- 37.

13:38.026 --> 13:41.487
- You'll be caught if you cheat.
- I've got 37. And you?

13:41.696 --> 13:42.822
52.

13:44.907 --> 13:46.909
You might be the one with the most.

13:47.160 --> 13:48.077
No way.

13:59.589 --> 14:01.591
- More salad?
- No.

14:12.018 --> 14:15.938
We're low on iodine 
and the antihistamines have expired.

14:16.105 --> 14:18.232
Also, we need more bandages.

14:18.441 --> 14:20.860
I'll give you a list.

14:21.069 --> 14:24.697
- Whatever you like.
- And black tint for your eyebrows.

14:24.906 --> 14:26.783
Didn't I get you some last week?

14:26.949 --> 14:31.746
I used it all. I need more.
I can't use blue.

14:31.954 --> 14:33.790
It would be unnatural.

14:38.961 --> 14:40.463
I'll get you some.

14:42.548 --> 14:44.967
- Do you want lemon?
- No, thanks.

14:46.427 --> 14:50.556
We'll be out of meat soon.
You need to bring more.

14:51.474 --> 14:55.812
Mom, could you pass me the phone? Please.

14:57.271 --> 14:58.564
Thank you.

14:59.941 --> 15:02.443
- Did you count your stickers?
- I have 76.

15:02.652 --> 15:04.153
I have 52.

15:04.320 --> 15:05.905
37.

15:06.614 --> 15:09.492
Girls, you have to try harder.

15:09.951 --> 15:12.161
Your brother is the winner again.

15:13.621 --> 15:17.667
That means he selects tonight's entertainment.

15:18.501 --> 15:20.628
But I have a surprise for you.

15:20.837 --> 15:22.421
Something unprecedented.

15:23.339 --> 15:26.843
The next prize will be
not one sticker, or two,

15:27.009 --> 15:28.678
but ten.

15:29.011 --> 15:31.514
So you must do your best.

15:32.515 --> 15:34.350
You see how important it is.

15:34.517 --> 15:36.102
Yes, absolutely.

15:37.103 --> 15:40.189
The winner tells us
how we spend the evening.

15:40.356 --> 15:41.441
I say video.

15:41.649 --> 15:43.943
We haven't watched one in a long time.

15:44.152 --> 15:45.695
It's a good opportunity.

16:01.127 --> 16:03.379
<i>Dad, may I water the plants too?</i>

16:04.714 --> 16:05.882
<i>Run!</i>

16:06.382 --> 16:08.551
<i>Be careful, slow down.</i>

16:11.387 --> 16:13.848
<i>Here, Dad, there's a dry herb.</i>

16:14.724 --> 16:17.393
<i>This is the problem.
There are more in there.</i>

16:17.643 --> 16:18.895
<i>Dad, there's an airplane!</i>

16:20.897 --> 16:24.025
<i>Can you bring a wet cloth
from the kitchen?</i>

16:24.233 --> 16:26.402
<i>Mom, where do we keep them?</i>

16:26.569 --> 16:29.322
<i>Under the sink, in the cupboard.</i>

16:31.157 --> 16:34.869
<i>Careful, don't bring a clean one.</i>

16:35.912 --> 16:38.164
<i>Look out, maybe it'll fall.</i>

16:41.501 --> 16:42.585
<i>Watch out!</i>

16:43.252 --> 16:46.088
<i>Mom, that was great!
Let me take a look.</i>

17:25.461 --> 17:27.546
I wash it much better than you.

17:30.132 --> 17:33.094
I also clean the tires and floor mats.

17:35.471 --> 17:39.308
And I never forget the air freshener. 
Only once.

17:39.725 --> 17:44.897
It smelled nice and I thought
I'd used some...

17:45.314 --> 17:46.607
already...

17:49.652 --> 17:51.487
You rarely remembered it

17:52.280 --> 17:54.657
and often didn't clean the mats

17:54.824 --> 17:58.953
when they had tough stains,
like mud and tar.

18:00.079 --> 18:03.666
I wish you'd see
that I wash it better than you.

18:03.833 --> 18:06.836
You'd have cried if you'd seen that.

18:14.010 --> 18:15.970
He's out at the fence again.

18:47.001 --> 18:49.045
He started throwing rocks at me.

18:49.295 --> 18:51.714
Your brother would never throw stones.

19:27.833 --> 19:30.419
Not yet, I'll tell you when.

19:38.594 --> 19:39.845
Hold on a while.

19:48.437 --> 19:49.939
Now spit it out.

20:05.955 --> 20:08.290
I wish it would fall.

20:09.792 --> 20:12.253
If it falls, I'll get it.

20:13.796 --> 20:17.550
Whoever deserves it will get it.

20:40.948 --> 20:42.950
- Good morning.
- How are you, Christina?

20:43.409 --> 20:45.578
Fine. My leg hurts a little.

20:45.786 --> 20:48.080
When are you coming again?

20:48.289 --> 20:52.293
I'll check the shifts.
Maybe one afternoon next week.

20:52.501 --> 20:54.336
Do you wear the perfume I gave you?

20:55.504 --> 20:57.173
Does it smell good?

20:57.423 --> 20:58.591
It does.

21:39.340 --> 21:41.509
Mr. Petrou called for you.

21:41.717 --> 21:43.802
- Did you water the yucca?
- Two weeks ago.

21:44.094 --> 21:46.722
- Do it every week.
- Yes, sir. Shall I call him?

21:46.889 --> 21:48.891
- No, I'll go.
- Yes, sir.

21:58.234 --> 22:01.987
My belly has been aching
since last night.

22:02.321 --> 22:04.323
Where exactly does it hurt?

22:08.994 --> 22:12.998
On the upper right side.
Could be an inflamed appendix.

22:13.207 --> 22:16.085
The vermiform appendix
is lower down on the right.

22:23.217 --> 22:24.760
- Here?
- No.

22:27.054 --> 22:28.889
- Here?
- No.

22:29.682 --> 22:31.600
- Does it hurt here?
- Yes.

22:33.102 --> 22:36.522
- Avoid eating fruit and vegetables.
- I drank some milk.

22:36.730 --> 22:40.693
It's okay.
You'd better not work out today.

22:41.277 --> 22:44.113
- No medication?
- You don't need any.

22:44.280 --> 22:48.033
Follow my instructions carefully
and you'll get well.

22:48.242 --> 22:52.204
Otherwise your condition will deteriorate.

22:53.622 --> 22:56.375
Get up. Can you play with me?

22:56.584 --> 22:58.627
We have about 20 minutes.

22:59.128 --> 23:02.548
I have a new anesthetic.
Do you want to try it out?

23:02.881 --> 23:03.883
Yes.

23:04.550 --> 23:07.595
The one who wakes up first
will be the winner.

23:13.309 --> 23:15.269
Don't put more on mine.

23:22.943 --> 23:25.321
One, two, three.

24:05.277 --> 24:08.989
It's nearly finished.
It needs floor tiles and lights.

24:09.198 --> 24:11.825
I can't decide which one I prefer.

24:17.957 --> 24:21.669
- I like these.
- I prefer those.

24:22.169 --> 24:23.921
Those are nice too.

24:24.713 --> 24:26.715
- How's your wife?
- Same.

24:27.174 --> 24:29.968
- Do you go out?
- No.

24:30.636 --> 24:33.889
I told you, you should.
Even if she's in a wheelchair.

24:34.139 --> 24:36.809
She's unwell.
And she doesn't like visitors.

24:37.017 --> 24:40.729
I've told her hundreds of times
to invite you for a beer.

24:40.896 --> 24:42.189
I understand.

24:42.398 --> 24:44.733
It's tragic what happened to her.

24:44.984 --> 24:47.361
It requires great psychological strength.

24:47.569 --> 24:50.572
In the picture, she looks energetic.

24:50.739 --> 24:52.491
She was a volleyball champion?

24:52.700 --> 24:53.742
Handball.

24:57.413 --> 24:58.706
These you said?

24:58.914 --> 25:01.000
Yes. The others are nice too.

25:37.244 --> 25:38.287
Hi, honey.

25:39.621 --> 25:42.541
I had a meeting. A meeting, yes.

25:43.542 --> 25:46.628
Did they go out? Or work out?

25:46.879 --> 25:50.632
Why, what's the matter?
Her belly or her stomach?

25:51.425 --> 25:52.634
Yes, it's cold outside.

26:33.634 --> 26:35.928
I'd like my dog back.

26:41.141 --> 26:44.269
Sorry, I can't do that.

26:44.478 --> 26:48.524
He's still on the second stage
of his training.

26:50.859 --> 26:52.444
I'll show you.

27:01.620 --> 27:03.956
First stage, second stage-

27:04.164 --> 27:05.707
where your dog is-

27:05.874 --> 27:08.710
third, fourth, fifth and final stage.

27:17.219 --> 27:19.012
Let me explain.

27:19.888 --> 27:21.515
Dogs are like clay

27:21.974 --> 27:26.145
and our job here is to mold them.

27:27.479 --> 27:29.356
A dog may be energetic,

27:30.399 --> 27:34.319
a fighter, cowardly, or gentle.

27:36.238 --> 27:41.076
All this requires work, patience
and care from us.

27:41.743 --> 27:44.913
Every dog is waiting for us

27:45.163 --> 27:47.541
to show it how it should behave.

27:48.500 --> 27:50.586
Do you understand?

27:50.919 --> 27:53.505
So the issue here

27:53.714 --> 27:58.760
is to decide together
how we want your dog to behave.

27:59.720 --> 28:04.391
Do we want an animal
or do we want a friend?

28:07.269 --> 28:11.106
Do we want a guard
who will respect us as his masters

28:11.940 --> 28:15.402
and do unhesitatingly 
whatever we ask of him?

28:16.403 --> 28:17.946
You see?

28:18.363 --> 28:19.448
Sure.

28:29.791 --> 28:30.792
Rex!

28:33.462 --> 28:34.546
Rex!

