1 minute 15 seconds.

30:56.897 --> 30:58.023
2 minutes.

31:05.072 --> 31:06.531
2 minutes 30 seconds.

31:09.785 --> 31:11.620
2 minutes 45 seconds.

31:20.295 --> 31:22.089
3 minutes 15 seconds.

31:31.556 --> 31:33.391
3 minutes 45 seconds.

31:51.159 --> 31:53.161
4 minutes 30 seconds.

32:01.670 --> 32:03.755
5 minutes 15 seconds.

32:09.511 --> 32:11.346
Five minutes 30 seconds.

33:48.443 --> 33:50.570
What do you mean you can't?

33:52.280 --> 33:53.782
I'm sorry.

33:54.699 --> 33:58.119
We're doing this for you,
not for me.

33:58.370 --> 33:59.704
I'm sorry.

34:00.789 --> 34:04.793
Try again but use your tongue.
There's no point otherwise.

34:14.803 --> 34:16.471
Don't tell Dad.

34:17.389 --> 34:19.224
- Do you feel disgusted?
- No.

34:19.599 --> 34:20.976
Then what?

34:22.978 --> 34:25.438
I prefer what we did last time.

34:41.413 --> 34:42.289
Hello.

34:45.333 --> 34:46.626
What are you doing?

34:47.168 --> 34:50.672
Cleaning the carpet to keep germs off it.

35:03.018 --> 35:06.521
- Do you want this headband?
- Yes, very much.

35:07.188 --> 35:09.024
What are you going to give me?

35:14.863 --> 35:17.699
How about this pencil?
It has an eraser on it.

35:17.949 --> 35:18.950
No.

35:25.624 --> 35:27.125
A tape measure?

35:28.376 --> 35:31.212
You press here and it reels in by itself.

35:32.005 --> 35:33.048
No.

35:44.225 --> 35:48.146
Come closer and lick for a while
and the headband is yours.

35:49.814 --> 35:51.191
Are you disgusted?

35:51.566 --> 35:52.650
No.

36:18.551 --> 36:21.262
- Do you want to dance?
- I don't feel like it.

36:21.513 --> 36:26.434
Besides, we don't have time.
We have to go meet Mom.

36:26.601 --> 36:30.772
Mom will be late. 
She's talking to herself again in her room.

36:31.356 --> 36:33.566
Are you afraid of Mom talking to herself?

36:33.775 --> 36:34.901
Not at all.

36:35.110 --> 36:36.528
- You are afraid.
- I'm not.

36:37.195 --> 36:38.446
- You are.
- No.

36:39.114 --> 36:42.367
You can't hear her.
She might be talking about you.

36:42.575 --> 36:43.952
Stop it.

36:50.875 --> 36:53.420
If I give you a present,
will you lick me?

36:53.628 --> 36:55.964
- What kind of present?
- A headband.

36:56.131 --> 36:57.590
I already have one.

36:57.799 --> 37:00.260
This one sparkles in the dark.

37:00.468 --> 37:02.303
What do you mean by sparkles?

37:03.096 --> 37:04.264
It lights up.

37:05.140 --> 37:06.599
Where did you get it?

37:06.808 --> 37:08.309
I can't tell you.

37:08.643 --> 37:11.730
Do our parents know
you have a headband like that?

37:13.565 --> 37:16.609
So, it could easily be yours.

37:18.820 --> 37:20.572
What do you want me to lick?

37:22.282 --> 37:23.491
My shoulder.

37:38.673 --> 37:42.135
Can you get some chocolate
if you pass by the shop?

37:42.343 --> 37:45.180
Don't go out of your way.

37:48.349 --> 37:49.684
Any kind.

37:58.151 --> 37:59.194
Me too.

39:05.426 --> 39:07.220
That isn't yours.

39:08.763 --> 39:10.014
Leave me alone.

40:23.212 --> 40:25.214
- Does it still hurt?
- Yes.

40:28.217 --> 40:32.388
You could ask Dad to get in the car
and fetch it for you.

40:32.597 --> 40:35.224
That's what I'd do if I were you.

40:35.433 --> 40:37.018
It's the only way.

40:41.689 --> 40:42.690
Dad!

40:46.861 --> 40:49.948
The eldest threw the airplane
over the fence.

40:50.198 --> 40:52.617
- Where?
- There, on the road.

40:53.785 --> 40:55.119
I'll try.

43:21.432 --> 43:23.351
How did it happen?

43:24.936 --> 43:26.437
What did you tell them?

43:28.022 --> 43:30.066
You did the right thing.

43:30.691 --> 43:32.401
I'll tell them as well.

43:33.361 --> 43:36.239
Yes, it's a good opportunity.

43:36.697 --> 43:37.740
<i>Yes.</i>

43:39.492 --> 43:43.037
<i>The temperature will rise
and the wind will drop.</i>

43:45.665 --> 43:47.834
<i>Five or six degrees.</i>

43:49.210 --> 43:50.545
<i>All right.</i>

43:52.505 --> 43:57.260
<i>No, it's time to put an end to this.
It's exhausting for everyone.</i>

